title: BRIEF-CHC Healthcare to pay cash dividend of T$1.1 per share
text: March 22, 2018 / 2:27 AM / Updated 10 hours ago BRIEF-CHC Healthcare to pay cash dividend of T$1.1 per share Reuters Staff 1 Min Read March 22 (Reuters) - CHC Healthcare Group * Says it will use undistributed profit to pay cash dividend of T$1.1 per share to shareholders for 2017 * Says it will pay cash dividend of T$153.9 million in total Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/72Efqc Further company coverage: (Beijing Headline News)
